Module org.example.cs_213_project_iii
Package impl

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
impl.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
Represents a fitness class in the gym management system. Each fitness class is associated with a specific class type, instructor, location, time, and lists of members and guests.
Author:
Sasanka Paththameistreege
